text: Jazy Garcia (born 14 July 1967) is a former cyclist from Guam. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Guamanian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Guam Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:American track cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
